Text: Bones you are the best-thank you..

I get a little embarassed sometimes...Soon as I come online each day I take a look at what you've uploaded and jump onto whatever you've shared.  Other than seeding, I haven't got much else to give by way of saying thanks...oh, unless you wanna jump on my Harley and I'll take you for a spin...lol.  Thanks, your time, energy and efforts are much appreciated... :-)
